<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Bereinigungslauf – Fehler – Propus</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f4f0;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }
    .card {
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.08), 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .card-header {
      background: #f8f7f4;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e6e0;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    }
    .card-header .logo { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #2a2a2a; }
    .card-body { padding: 2rem; text-align: center; }
    .error-icon {
      width: 52px; height: 52px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #fdecea;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
    }
    h1 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: .75rem; color: #111; }
    p { color: #666; font-size: .9rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .footer {
      padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #f0ede8;
      font-size: .8rem;
      color: #888;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer strong { color: #444; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <span class="logo">Propus Team</span>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="error-icon">⚠️</div>
      <h1>Link nicht gültig</h1>
      <p><%= error || 'Dieser Link ist ungültig, abgelaufen oder wurde bereits verwendet. Bitte kontaktieren Sie uns direkt.' %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <strong>Freundliche Grüsse</strong><br>
      Ihr Propus Team
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
